p.span: Thank you for your interest in the Durand-Arkansaw School District. On behalf of the school board, administration, faculty, staff and students of our district, I want to welcome you to our district and encourage you to learn more about the many incredible programs and services we offer for students. Our website is designed to be a quick and easy way for you to learn about our school district and get important information.

to be the District Administrator of this wonderful district. Over the past seven years I have been impressed with the passion for education by those involved in the district and the commitment by the community towards
We look forward to providing your children with a challenging education that builds academic competence, encourages creativity, promotes lifelong learning, and fosters respect for self and others.

As always, we will continue in our quest to be the best district in the nation. Once again, thank you for your continued support of our district and we hope to see you this year at the many events where our students showcase their many talents.

span.br: The school district website is a great source for information. To find information specific to Caddie Woodlawn Elementary School or Durand Middle/High School, select the school you want from the drop-down menu on the district homepage.
